title: Best Of (Cowboys first victory with Rush, Evans and Lattimore fight, Tua’s 6 TDs in comeback win)
description:
00:00 Cowboys defeat Burrow and the Bengals 20-17. Can Cooper Rush hold it down until Dak returns?
13:39 Tampa Brady finally defeats the Saints 20-10. Did the Evans and Lattimore fight ignite Bucs' victory?
30:21 Tua stuns the Ravens with 6 TDs in victory. How are the Dolphins looking after a 21-point comeback?
